{"title":"在树莓派4B上编写裸机操作系统(三)","date":"2021-05-06T10:28:21.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"May 6, 2021","L":"05/06/2021","MM-DD":"05-06"},"link":"rpi_osdev/rpi_osdev_3","comments":true,"tags":["操作系统,树莓派"],"categories":["树莓派操作系统开发"],"updated":"2021-05-06T15:10:44.600Z","content":"<h1 id=\"在树莓派4b上编写裸机操作系统-(part-3)\">在树莓派4B上编写裸机操作系统 (Part 3)<a title=\"#在树莓派4b上编写裸机操作系统-(part-3)\" href=\"#在树莓派4b上编写裸机操作系统-(part-3)\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"让我们在main()中做些什么\">让我们在<code>main()</code>中做些什么<a title=\"#让我们在main()中做些什么\" href=\"#让我们在main()中做些什么\"></a></h2>\n<p>到目前为止，我们的操作系统只能输出黑屏。我们如何确定我们的代码真的在运行？让我们做一些更有趣的事情，以真正证明我们可以控制硬件。</p>\n<p>通常，程序员要学习的第一件事就是在屏幕上打印&quot;Hello world!&quot;。但是，在裸机开发中，在屏幕上打印可能是一个巨大的挑战，因此，我们决定先从一些更简单的事情开始做。</p>\n<h2 id=\"uart简介\">UART简介<a title=\"#uart简介\" href=\"#uart简介\"></a></h2>\n<p>我们可以从操作系统&quot;发送消息&quot;的最简单方法是通过UART或串行通信电路。UART代表Universal Asynchronous Receiver/Transmitter(通用异步接收器/发送器)，它是一个非常古老且相当简单的接口，仅使用两条线在两个设备之间进行通信。在USB出现之前，我们以这种方式连接诸如鼠标，打印机和调制解调器之类的设备。</p>\n<p>我们将使用开发机直接连接到你的树莓派，并让它发送&quot;Hello world!&quot;消息到你的开发机，你的开发机会将其打印到屏幕上。</p>\n<p>你可能会用到:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>一条USB到串口转换线（注：原文此处给出英国亚马逊购买地址，大家自行某宝购买）</li>\n<li>下载并安装转换线对应的驱动（注：原文给出原作者所用转换线对应驱动下载地址，这里大家自行问某宝店家要，也有可能不需要安装额外驱动）</li>\n<li>下载并安装<a href=\"https://www.chiark.greenend.org.uk/~sgtatham/putty/latest.html\" target=\"_blank\">PuTTY</a></li>\n<li>如果你使用Mac，你可以安装<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/gb/app/serialtools/id611021963?mt=12\" target=\"_blank\">Serial Tools</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果你想了解更多串口通信的背景知识，你可以查阅<a href=\"https://learn.sparkfun.com/tutorials/serial-communication/all\" target=\"_blank\">SparkFun website</a>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"连接你的开发机和树莓派\">连接你的开发机和树莓派<a title=\"#连接你的开发机和树莓派\" href=\"#连接你的开发机和树莓派\"></a></h2>\n<p>如果你已经成功安装驱动，那么把你的转换线连接到开发机，你会发现在&quot;控制面板&quot;，“设备管理器”,“端口”，你应该可以看到类似于UART，Serial之类的字样（注：取决于不同产品的名称）。如果你可以看见，说明连接线正常工作。</p>\n<p>这是我电脑上的显示:</p>\n<p><img src=\"images/3-helloworld-ctlpanel.png\" alt=\"Windows Control Panel with cable installed\" class=\"φbs\"></p>\n<p>记住设备管理器中刚刚看见设备名后面括号中的COMx - 对于我来说是COM5。</p>\n<p>对于同一款转换线，它在Mac下不需要安装驱动（注：不保证大家在某宝买的在Mac下不需要安装驱动）。</p>\n<p>现在，我们需要知道转换线如何连接树莓派一端。你需要找到<strong>GPIO pins</strong>，一共有40个，在Raspberry Pi copyright字样的上方。</p>\n<p>下图显示了需要连接的位置。 黑线接地（引脚6）上，白线接在TXD上（GPIO 14/引脚8），绿线接RXD上（GPIO 15/引脚10）。当我们使用专用电源为树莓派供电时，请确保<strong>不要连接红线</strong>。（注：不同产品线的颜色不一样，简单来说转换线端RXD接树莓派TXD，转换线端TXD接树莓派RXD，GND接地，我们还可以从USB端口为我们的板子取电，但是树莓派有独立供电，所以不需要接5V或3.3V供电）</p>\n<p><img src=\"images/3-helloworld-pinloc.png\" alt=\"GPIO location\" class=\"φbs\"></p>\n<p>这是我的板子接好之后的样子:</p>\n<p><img src=\"images/3-helloworld-cable.jpg\" alt=\"GPIO photo with cable connected\" class=\"φbs\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"设置putty\">设置PuTTY<a title=\"#设置putty\" href=\"#设置putty\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>在开发机上启动PuTTY</li>\n<li>在左边菜单中点击&quot;Session&quot;</li>\n<li>将&quot;Connection type&quot;设置为Serial</li>\n<li>点击左边菜单 Connection&quot;中的&quot;Serial&quot;</li>\n<li>将&quot;Serial line to connect to&quot;设置为我们刚刚记住的COMx，对于我来说是COM5</li>\n<li>将&quot;Speed (baud)&quot;设置为115200</li>\n<li>确认&quot;Data bits&quot;为8, &quot;Stop bits&quot;为1, &quot;Parity&quot;和&quot;Flow control&quot;为None</li>\n<li>回到&quot;Session&quot;</li>\n<li>在下方&quot;Saved Sessions&quot;输入给你的配置去一个名字，然后点击Save保存配置</li>\n<li>你现在可以双击刚刚保存的配置 - 然后你会看到一个黑窗口</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果你使用了不同的终端模拟器，你需要根据其对应的用法进行相同的设置，例如Serial Tools on Mac可以参照<a href=\"https://www.w7ay.net/site/Applications/Serial%20Tools/\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>设置。</p>\n<h2 id=\"config.txt配置\">config.txt配置<a title=\"#config.txt配置\" href=\"#config.txt配置\"></a></h2>\n<p>我们在最开始的教程里面曾经提到过，为了让我的Raspbian能够在我的电视上输出内容，我编辑了SD卡中的 <em>config.txt</em>。现在我们需要在这个文件中增加一行内容让UART连接变得可靠。</p>\n<p>UART通信是时序强相关的，所以我们需要严格保证发送端与接收端的收发速率相等。我们在PuTTY中将波特率设置为了115200，所以我们需要在树莓派4B上进行类似的设置。通常来说，UART芯片具有独立的时钟晶振。对于树莓派，它具有一共6个UART芯片，其中<strong>UART0,UART2-5</strong>为PL011芯片，具有独立时钟。而<strong>UART1</strong>为miniUART，它与CPU共享时钟信号。默认来说，树莓派的bootloader将UART0映射到蓝牙接口，UART1映射到GPIO接口，因此我们无法保证发送端（树莓派）的速率始终为115200，这取决于CPU的繁忙程度。</p>\n<p>你可以在 <em>config.txt</em> 中新增下面一行内容用于将UART0映射到GPIO：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">enable_uart=<span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>更多信息可以参考<a href=\"https://www.raspberrypi.org/documentation/configuration/uart.md\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"在你的代码中操作uart\">在你的代码中操作UART<a title=\"#在你的代码中操作uart\" href=\"#在你的代码中操作uart\"></a></h2>\n<p>首先，在你的 <em>kernel.c</em> 中新增几个函数调用：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"meta-string\">&quot;io.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    uart_init();</span><br><span class=\"line\">    uart_writeText(<span class=\"string\">&quot;Hello world!\\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> (<span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后，我们新增一个头文件 <em>io.h</em>。这可以帮助我们分离代码，将新增代码放在在 <em>kernel.c</em> 文件之外。</p>\n<p>你会注意到我们的<code>main()</code>函数中新增加了几行代码。首先，我们调用一个函数来初始化UART，然后调用另一个函数来编写&quot;Hello world!&quot;。字符串末尾<code>\\n</code>用于换行，就像在文字处理器中按Enter一样！</p>\n<p>这是我们新增的 <em>io.h</em> 中的内容：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">uart_init</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">uart_writeText</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">char</span> *buffer)</span></span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这是一个非常简短的文件，带有两个<strong>函数定义</strong>。<code>uart_init()</code>是一个空函数，没有参数，就像<code>main()</code>一样。这意味着它不需要传入任何参数也不需要返回任何数据。你会注意到<code>uart_writeText</code>也是一个void函数，但是它需要一个参数，因为我们需要告诉它要它需要输出什么内容。</p>\n<p>我们将上面两个函数的具体实现放入一个新文件 <em>io.c</em> 中：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br><span class=\"line\">79</span><br><span class=\"line\">80</span><br><span class=\"line\">81</span><br><span class=\"line\">82</span><br><span class=\"line\">83</span><br><span class=\"line\">84</span><br><span class=\"line\">85</span><br><span class=\"line\">86</span><br><span class=\"line\">87</span><br><span class=\"line\">88</span><br><span class=\"line\">89</span><br><span class=\"line\">90</span><br><span class=\"line\">91</span><br><span class=\"line\">92</span><br><span class=\"line\">93</span><br><span class=\"line\">94</span><br><span class=\"line\">95</span><br><span class=\"line\">96</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// GPIO</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">enum</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    PERIPHERAL_BASE = <span class=\"number\">0xFE000000</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    GPFSEL0         = PERIPHERAL_BASE + <span class=\"number\">0x200000</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    GPSET0          = PERIPHERAL_BASE + <span class=\"number\">0x20001C</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    GPCLR0          = PERIPHERAL_BASE + <span class=\"number\">0x200028</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    GPPUPPDN0       = PERIPHERAL_BASE + <span class=\"number\">0x2000E4</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">enum</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    GPIO_MAX_PIN       = <span class=\"number\">53</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    GPIO_FUNCTION_ALT5 = <span class=\"number\">2</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">enum</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    Pull_None = <span class=\"number\">0</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">mmio_write</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">long</span> reg, <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> val)</span> </span>&#123; *(<span class=\"keyword\">volatile</span> <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> *)reg = val; &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">mmio_read</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">long</span> reg)</span> </span>&#123; <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> *(<span class=\"keyword\">volatile</span> <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> *)reg; &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">gpio_call</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> pin_number, <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> value, <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> base, <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> field_size, <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> field_max)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> field_mask = (<span class=\"number\">1</span> &lt;&lt; field_size) - <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (pin_number &gt; field_max) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (value &gt; field_mask) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">0</span>; </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> num_fields = <span class=\"number\">32</span> / field_size;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> reg = base + ((pin_number / num_fields) * <span class=\"number\">4</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> shift = (pin_number % num_fields) * field_size;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> curval = mmio_read(reg);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    curval &amp;= ~(field_mask &lt;&lt; shift);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    curval |= value &lt;&lt; shift;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mmio_write(reg, curval);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">gpio_set</span>     <span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> pin_number, <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> value)</span> </span>&#123; <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> gpio_call(pin_number, value, GPSET0, <span class=\"number\">1</span>, GPIO_MAX_PIN); &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">gpio_clear</span>   <span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> pin_number, <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> value)</span> </span>&#123; <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> gpio_call(pin_number, value, GPCLR0, <span class=\"number\">1</span>, GPIO_MAX_PIN); &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">gpio_pull</span>    <span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> pin_number, <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> value)</span> </span>&#123; <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> gpio_call(pin_number, value, GPPUPPDN0, <span class=\"number\">2</span>, GPIO_MAX_PIN); &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">gpio_function</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> pin_number, <span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> value)</span> </span>&#123; <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> gpio_call(pin_number, value, GPFSEL0, <span class=\"number\">3</span>, GPIO_MAX_PIN); &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">gpio_useAsAlt5</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> pin_number)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    gpio_pull(pin_number, Pull_None);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    gpio_function(pin_number, GPIO_FUNCTION_ALT5);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// UART</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">enum</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    AUX_BASE        = PERIPHERAL_BASE + <span class=\"number\">0x215000</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AUX_ENABLES     = AUX_BASE + <span class=\"number\">4</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AUX_MU_IO_REG   = AUX_BASE + <span class=\"number\">64</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AUX_MU_IER_REG  = AUX_BASE + <span class=\"number\">68</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AUX_MU_IIR_REG  = AUX_BASE + <span class=\"number\">72</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AUX_MU_LCR_REG  = AUX_BASE + <span class=\"number\">76</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AUX_MU_MCR_REG  = AUX_BASE + <span class=\"number\">80</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AUX_MU_LSR_REG  = AUX_BASE + <span class=\"number\">84</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AUX_MU_CNTL_REG = AUX_BASE + <span class=\"number\">96</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AUX_MU_BAUD_REG = AUX_BASE + <span class=\"number\">104</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    AUX_UART_CLOCK  = <span class=\"number\">500000000</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    UART_MAX_QUEUE  = <span class=\"number\">16</span> * <span class=\"number\">1024</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">define</span> AUX_MU_BAUD(baud) ((AUX_UART_CLOCK/(baud*8))-1)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">uart_init</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mmio_write(AUX_ENABLES, <span class=\"number\">1</span>); <span class=\"comment\">//enable UART1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    mmio_write(AUX_MU_IER_REG, <span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mmio_write(AUX_MU_CNTL_REG, <span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mmio_write(AUX_MU_LCR_REG, <span class=\"number\">3</span>); <span class=\"comment\">//8 bits</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    mmio_write(AUX_MU_MCR_REG, <span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mmio_write(AUX_MU_IER_REG, <span class=\"number\">0</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mmio_write(AUX_MU_IIR_REG, <span class=\"number\">0xC6</span>); <span class=\"comment\">//disable interrupts</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    mmio_write(AUX_MU_BAUD_REG, AUX_MU_BAUD(<span class=\"number\">115200</span>));</span><br><span class=\"line\">    gpio_useAsAlt5(<span class=\"number\">14</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    gpio_useAsAlt5(<span class=\"number\">15</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mmio_write(AUX_MU_CNTL_REG, <span class=\"number\">3</span>); <span class=\"comment\">//enable RX/TX</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">uart_isWriteByteReady</span><span class=\"params\">()</span> </span>&#123; <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> mmio_read(AUX_MU_LSR_REG) &amp; <span class=\"number\">0x20</span>; &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">uart_writeByteBlockingActual</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">char</span> ch)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> (!uart_isWriteByteReady()); </span><br><span class=\"line\">    mmio_write(AUX_MU_IO_REG, (<span class=\"keyword\">unsigned</span> <span class=\"keyword\">int</span>)ch);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">uart_writeText</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">char</span> *buffer)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> (*buffer) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (*buffer == <span class=\"string\">&#x27;\\n&#x27;</span>) uart_writeByteBlockingActual(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;\\r&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">       uart_writeByteBlockingActual(*buffer++);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>你会看到我们在 <em>io.h</em> 头文件中定义的两个函数的具体实现代码以及一些不需要对外暴露细节的辅助函数。在下一个教程中，我将解释这段代码中发生的事情，但是现在我们可以直接先编译运行这段代码。</p>\n<p>将你的 <em>io.c</em> 与 <em>io.h</em> 放到与 <em>kernel.c</em> 同一个目录下，然后使用<code>make</code>编译你的OS。</p>\n<p>然后:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>将你的 <em>kernel8.img</em> 复制到SD卡的根目录下，然后将SD卡插入到你的树莓派4B</li>\n<li>确保你的转换线正确连接</li>\n<li>启动你的终端模拟器（例如PuTTY）并连接到串口</li>\n<li>启动你的树莓派4B</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果一切正常，你应该在几秒钟之后在PuTTY的黑窗口上看见&quot;Hello world!&quot;。</p>\n<p><em>这个输出消息证明了你的OS在正常工作。至少先动手尝试一下！</em></p>\n<p><a href=\"./rpi_osdev/rpi_osdev_4\">Go to part4-miniuart &gt;</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"在树莓派4B上编写裸机操作系统(二)","link":"rpi_osdev/rpi_osdev_2"},"next":{"title":"基于UEFI的操作系统开发(零) 前言","link":"osdev/osdev_0"},"plink":"http://superfish.me/rpi_osdev/rpi_osdev_3/","toc":[{"id":"在树莓派4b上编写裸机操作系统-(part-3)","title":"在树莓派4B上编写裸机操作系统 (Part 3)","index":"1","children":[{"id":"让我们在main()中做些什么","title":"让我们在main()中做些什么","index":"1.1"},{"id":"uart简介","title":"UART简介","index":"1.2"},{"id":"连接你的开发机和树莓派","title":"连接你的开发机和树莓派","index":"1.3"},{"id":"设置putty","title":"设置PuTTY","index":"1.4"},{"id":"config.txt配置","title":"config.txt配置","index":"1.5"},{"id":"在你的代码中操作uart","title":"在你的代码中操作UART","index":"1.6"}]}],"reading_time":"2273 words in 15 min"}